## Hunt schema v5

```json
{
  "id": "string",                 // required, stable, unique
  "title": "string",              // required
  "description": "string",        // optional ("" default)
  "metadata": {                   // optional, object
    "tags": ["string"],
    "estimatedDuration": "number",
    "difficulty": "string",
    "author": "string",
    "createdAt": "string",
    "updatedAt": "string",
    "_reserved": {}
  },
  "nodes": [ /* NodeSchemaV5 */ ],
  "items": [ /* ItemSchemaV5 */ ],
  "isPublic": "boolean",          // required (false default)
  "accessCode": "string|null",    // optional
  "version": "number",            // required, hunt content version (increments on major edit)
  "schemaVersion": "number",      // required, fixed = 5 for V5
  "_reserved": {}                 // reserved for future top-level fields
}
```

**Rules:**

- **Required:** `id`, `title`, `nodes`, `items`, `isPublic`, `version`, `schemaVersion`.
- **Optional with defaults:** `description` → `""`, `metadata` → `{}`, `accessCode` → `null`.
- **Immutable meaning:** `id` is permanent; `schemaVersion` defines how to interpret the hunt.

---

## Node schema v5

```json
{
  "id": "string",                 // required, unique within hunt
  "type": "string",               // required, e.g. "story", "puzzle", "wordPuzzle", "gem"
  "title": "string",              // required
  "body": "string",               // optional ("" default)
  "nextNodeId": "string|null",    // optional, null = end or type-specific behavior

  "ui": {                         // UI/visual contract
    "background": "string|null",  // asset key or URL
    "textColor": "string|null",   // CSS color
    "accentColor": "string|null", // CSS color
    "font": "string|null",        // font identifier
    "layout": "string|null"       // reserved for future layouts
  },

  "timer": {                      // optional
    "enabled": "boolean",
    "seconds": "number",
    "onExpireNodeId": "string|null" // fallback if timer expires
  },

  "gating": {                     // optional
    "requiresItems": ["string"],  // item IDs
    "requiresState": {            // simple key/value conditions
      "key": "value"
    },
    "failNodeId": "string|null"   // where to go if gating fails
  },

  "rewards": {                    // optional, Inventory C-ready
    "items": [
      {
        "itemId": "string",
        "quantity": "number"
      }
    ],
    "state": {
      "key": "value"
    }
  },

  "typeData": {                   // type-specific payload
    // story: { ... }
    // puzzle: { ... }
    // wordPuzzle: { ... }
    // gem: { choices: [...], etc. }
  },

  "metadata": {                   // optional
    "debugLabel": "string",
    "authorNote": "string",
    "_reserved": {}
  },

  "_reserved": {}                 // reserved for future node-level fields
}
```

**Rules:**

- **Required:** `id`, `type`, `title`.
- **Optional with defaults:**  
  - `body` → `""`, `nextNodeId` → `null`.  
  - `ui`, `timer`, `gating`, `rewards`, `typeData`, `metadata` → `{}` if missing.
- **Type safety:**  
  - `typeData` is **the only place** type-specific fields live.  
  - NodeType Interface will operate on `type`, `typeData`, and shared fields.

